[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    1488[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;101;115;126m<!--[38;2;101;115;126m TODO: replace illustrative figures with measured results from the deployment. The ranges above are typical for telehealth speech-to-text deployments but vary substantially with institutional configuration, patient demographics, audio quality distribution, and visit type mix [38;2;101;115;126m-->[K
